Dependency Tree

  • net.sourceforge.reb4j:net.sourceforge.reb4j.scala:bundle:1.1.0
    reb4j Scala Library

    Description: The purpose of reb4j is to provide a pure Java wrapper around the regular expression syntax provided by the JRE's java.util.regex.Pattern class in order to facilitate programmatic construction of regular expressions while taking advantage of compile-time syntax checking. This sub-project contains the Scala implementation of reb4j.

    URL: http://reggert.github.com/reb4j/net.sourceforge.reb4j.scala

    Project License: GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0
